<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>מערכת ניהול בית ספר</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            direction: rtl;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .registration-card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 100%;
        }
        
        .registration-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .registration-card .card-body {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .registration-card .display-1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .teacher-card, .student-card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .teacher-card:hover, .student-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        .teacher-card {
            border-right: 5px solid #667eea;
        }
        
        .student-card {
            border-right: 5px solid #28a745;
        }
        
        .badge-class {
            background-color: #667eea;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #333;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: #999;
        }
        
        .loading-spinner {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            color: #999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1>🏫 מערכת ניהול בית ספר</h1>
        <p>ניהול תלמידות ומורות בקלות ובדיוק</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container-lg">
        <!-- Registration Section -->
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card registration-card bg-light">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="display-1">🎓</div>
                        <h3 class="card-title mb-3">הרשמת תלמידה</h3>
                        <p class="card-text mb-4 text-muted">הוסף תלמידה חדשה למערכת</p>
                        <a href="/register-student" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">להרשמה</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card registration-card bg-light">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="display-1">👩‍🏫</div>
                        <h3 class="card-title mb-3">כניסת מורה</h3>
                        <p class="card-text mb-4 text-muted">כניסה למערכת המורה</p>
                        <a href="/login-teacher" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">כניסה</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>